log
@join tg-ports-devel branch into HEAD
@
text
@$MirOS: ports/infrastructure/install/patch-bsd_sys_mk,v 1.2 2005/04/12 18:18:59 tg Exp $

This patch is necessary for using <bsd.port.mk> and
<bsd.lib.mk> within MirPorts.

Applies to (at least):
* OPENBSD_2_8
* OPENBSD_2_9
* OPENBSD_3_0
* OPENBSD_3_1
* OPENBSD_3_2
* OPENBSD_3_3
* OPENBSD_3_4
* OPENBSD_3_5
* OPENBSD_3_6
* OPENBSD_3_7
* MIRBSD_7ter
* MIRBSD_7quater

Not needed when using portable MirMake with MirPorts.

Index: bsd.sys.mk
===================================================================
